  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "chapterTitle": "25",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26401225_29_4325-4769",
          "range": "4325-4740",
          "rangeStart": 4325,
          "rangeEnd": 4740,
          "markText": "我站起来，踉踉跄跄跌出去，肚子差点撞到对面的墙。我只好躺回去，慢慢调整自己的呼吸。我浑身刺痛，冒着大汗。我能感到小汗珠从额头慢慢滑落，沿鼻翼一直流到嘴角。我傻乎乎地舔了舔汗珠。\n我再次坐好，把双脚稳稳踩到地上，然后站起来。\n“好了，马洛，”我在牙缝中间说道，“你是个硬汉，一个六英尺高的铁人。你净重190磅，脸也洗过了；肌肉结实，下巴不是玻璃做的。你能做到。你被放倒两次，脖子被掐过，下巴被枪托打过。你浑身都被注射了麻醉剂，糊涂得像两只发疯的华尔兹老鼠￼。但这一切又算得上什么呢？不过是家常便饭罢了。现在，让我们瞧瞧你有多像个硬汉，先把裤子穿上。”\n",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1635339788,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-10-27 21:03:08",
          "chapterUid": 29,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=4325&rangeEnd=4740",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=4325&rangeEnd=4740"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_9_4380-4398",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4380-4398",
      "markText": "她假笑了起来，样子跟洗衣盆一样可爱。",
      "totalCount": 368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4380&rangeEnd=4398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4380&rangeEnd=4398"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_45_3089-3120",
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "range": "3089-3120",
      "markText": "今天的天气凉爽而晴朗，你可以看得很远，但不及魏尔玛去的地方远。",
      "totalCount": 352,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3089&rangeEnd=3120",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3089&rangeEnd=3120"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_22_2783-2838",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "2783-2838",
      "markText": "宅子本身没什么了不起的，规模比白金汉宫小一点吧，楼体颜色放在加州显得过于灰暗了，窗子也没有克莱斯勒大厦上的多。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2783&rangeEnd=2838",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2783&rangeEnd=2838"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_22_4398-4419",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "4398-4419",
      "markText": "她冲我抛出一个让我感觉自己财力有限的微笑。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=4398&rangeEnd=4419",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=4398&rangeEnd=4419"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_38_1408-1475",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "1408-1475",
      "markText": "我需要喝一杯，需要上很多人寿保险，需要一个假期，需要一个位于乡间的家，但我有的只是一件外衣、一顶帽子和一把枪。我穿戴整齐后离开了房间。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1408&rangeEnd=1475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1408&rangeEnd=1475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_13_1999-2032",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1999-2032",
      "markText": "这辆进口大轿车自己开着自己，我握着方向盘坐在那里，不过是摆摆样子。",
      "totalCount": 220,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1999&rangeEnd=2032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1999&rangeEnd=2032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401225_12_727-794",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "727-794",
      "markText": "所谓蒙特马·维斯塔区，指的是几串大小形状各异的房子，沿山脊颤颤巍巍地垂挂下来——感觉那座山打个喷嚏，就能把它们震到海滩上的盒装午餐里。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401225&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=727&rangeEnd=794",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/895323c07192d9c9895d21a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=727&rangeEnd=794"
